#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for <button>Create account</button></h2>
If:
<ul>
<li>The account name is filled in
<li>The password is filled in
<li>The retyped password is filled in and matches the password
<li>The full name is filled in
<li>Any captcha presented is correct
<li>All other required fields are filled in
</ul>
The <button>Create account</button> will create an account and log you
in to that account.  Upon creation, this account will have the priviledge
of being able to run this software, but will probably not have the ability
to run other Brightsands software without administrator intervention.
